2026-05-13T03:28:07.9286686Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-13T03:28:07.9287425Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-13T03:28:07.9288195Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-05-13T03:28:07.9288817Z 19        we only request it when the toggle is on.
2026-05-13T03:28:07.9289553Z 20    -->
